# Shell scripts and Dockerfiles must stay LF so they run inside Linux containers
# and via bash — this repo is often checked out on Windows (core.autocrlf=true),
# which would otherwise give them CRLF and break `#!/usr/bin/env bash` as `bash\r`.
*.sh            text eol=lf
Dockerfile*     text eol=lf
*.bash          text eol=lf
